0.1.0.name: wordpress/feedburner-stats-by-devmdcom
0.1.0.description:
Say hello to our new WordPress plugin that enables you to get a great insight into your FeedBurner feed, along with information and statistics about the subscribers, views, clicks, feed item information and chronological statistics.

The idea of this plugin is to give you access to your FeedBurner statistics, right from the WordPress admin panel, allowing you to monitor your day to day feed performance.

The plugin uses our new coding project, the FeedBurner Awareness PHP API to access the data from FeedBurner and the Google Visualization API for the colorful and interactive historical representations of your feed subscribers, reach and hits.

The plugin requires PHP 5.1 or higher!!!
